About the game:

Save farm animals from their cruel human masters and take them on a much-needed vacation. Use your superior alien powers to thwart human attempts to keep the happy livestock captive. Enjoy hilarious sound effects with 8 kinds of animals to save in beautiful scenery. See comic snapshots of vacationing aliens and liberated farm animals. It's easy to play and wildly addictive!
